/* ============================================================
   $StyleSheetUser — your custom CSS goes here.

   The active theme's stylesheet is composed as three cascade
   layers: base → theme → user. Anything you put in this file
   lives in the `user` layer and overrides any theme rule,
   regardless of selector specificity. Use it for personal tweaks
   without forking a theme.

   Example:
     :root {
       --col6: hotpink;   // recolour every link
     }
     div.tiddler { max-width: 1100px; }
   ============================================================ */
